# Medical Center Management System - API Documentation

This document outlines the RESTful API endpoints for the system, mapped directly to the implemented user stories.

---

## 1. Authentication & Users (`/api/users`)

### `POST /api/auth/login`
Authenticates a user and returns a token.
**Parameters:**
| Name | Type | In | Required | Description |
|------|------|----|----------|-------------|
| email | string | body | Yes | User email |
| password | string | body | Yes | User password |

**Response:**
- `200 OK`: `{ "token": "jwt...", "user": { "id": 1, "role": "Doctor" } }`
- `401 Unauthorized`: Invalid credentials

### `GET /api/users`
*(US-ADM 01)* Get all users in the system (Admin only).
**Response:**
- `200 OK`: Array of user objects

### `POST /api/users`
*(US-ADM 02)* Add a new staff member (Admin only).
**Parameters:**
| Name | Type | In | Required | Description |
|------|------|----|----------|-------------|
| name, email, contact, role, password | string | body | Yes | User details |

**Response:**
- `201 Created`: User created successfully

