## 2. Patients (`/api/patients`)

### `POST /api/patients`
*(US-REC 02)* Register a new patient.
**Parameters:**
| Name | Type | In | Required | Description |
|------|------|----|----------|-------------|
| name, email, contactNo, address, dob | string | body | Yes | Patient details |

**Response:** `201 Created`: `{ "patientId": 123 }`

### `GET /api/patients/:id/family`
*(US-PAT 06, US-DOC 04)* Access family members' accounts/profiles.
**Response:** `200 OK`: Array of related patient objects

### `GET /api/patients/:id/medical-data`
*(US-DOC 03)* Access a patient's complete medical data (prescriptions, tests, notes).
**Response:** `200 OK`: Complete patient history payload

---

## 3. Appointments (`/api/appointments`)

### `POST /api/appointments`
*(US-PAT 01, US-REC 03)* Book an appointment.
**Parameters:**
| Name | Type | In | Required | Description |
|------|------|----|----------|-------------|
| patientId | int | body | Yes | ID of patient |
| doctorId | int | body | Yes | ID of selected doctor |
| date | string | body | Yes | Appointment date (YYYY-MM-DD) |
| time | string | body | Yes | Appointment time (HH:MM) |

**Response:** `201 Created`: Appointment object

### `GET /api/appointments`
*(US-PAT 02, US-REC 01)* View appointments (filters vary by role: date, week, month).
**Parameters:**
| Name | Type | In | Required | Description |
|------|------|----|----------|-------------|
| filter | string | query | No | 'today', 'week', 'month' |

**Response:** `200 OK`: Array of appointment objects

### `PUT /api/appointments/:id/status`
*(US-REC 04, US-REC 05)* Update appointment status (Cancel, Checked-in).
**Parameters:**
| Name | Type | In | Required | Description |
|------|------|----|----------|-------------|
| status | string | body | Yes | 'Cancelled' or 'Arrived' |

**Response:** `200 OK`: Updated appointment

### `GET /api/appointments/stats/count`
*(US-DOC 02)* Check average number of appointments (daily, monthly, annual).
**Response:** `200 OK`: `{ "daily": 15, "monthly": 420, "annual": 5100 }`

---

## 4. Clinical Care (`/api/clinical`)

### `POST /api/clinical/notes`
*(US-DOC 05)* Add clinical notes about a patient.
**Parameters:**
| Name | Type | In | Required | Description |
|------|------|----|----------|-------------|
| patientId | int | body | Yes | Patient ID |
| notesText | string | body | Yes | The clinical observations |

**Response:** `201 Created`: Note object

