## 5. Lab Tests & Reports (`/api/labs`)

### `POST /api/labs/tests`
*(US-DOC 06)* Recommend lab tests for a patient.
**Parameters:**
| Name | Type | In | Required | Description |
|------|------|----|----------|-------------|
| patientId | int | body | Yes | Patient ID |
| testName | string | body | Yes | Name of requested test |

**Response:** `201 Created`: Lab test request

### `GET /api/labs/tests/pending`
*(US-LAB 01)* View all pending lab test requests.
**Response:** `200 OK`: Array of pending test requests

### `POST /api/labs/reports`
*(US-LAB 02)* Upload lab report to a request.
**Parameters:**
| Name | Type | In | Required | Description |
|------|------|----|----------|-------------|
| testId | int | form | Yes | ID of the lab test |
| reportFile | file | form | Yes | Physical PDF file |
| resultText | string | form | No | Textual result |

**Response:** `201 Created`: Report uploaded

### `GET /api/labs/reports/patient/:patientId`
*(US-PAT 03)* Check patient lab reports.
**Response:** `200 OK`: Array of lab reports with download URLs

