## 6. Prescriptions & Pharmacy (`/api/pharmacy`)

### `GET /api/pharmacy/inventory`
*(US-PHR 01, US-PHR 08)* See current inventory of all medicines (highlights out-of-stock).
**Response:** `200 OK`: Array of medicine objects

### `POST /api/pharmacy/inventory`
*(US-PHR 03)* Add new medicines to the system.
**Response:** `201 Created`: Added medicine object

### `PUT /api/pharmacy/inventory/:medicineId/stock`
*(US-PHR 04, US-PHR 02)* Update inventory count when restocking / reordering.
**Parameters:**
| Name | Type | In | Required | Description |
|------|------|----|----------|-------------|
| stockCount | int | body | Yes | New stock volume |

**Response:** `200 OK`: Updated inventory object

### `POST /api/pharmacy/prescriptions`
*(US-DOC 07)* Issue new prescriptions.
**Parameters:**
| Name | Type | In | Required | Description |
|------|------|----|----------|-------------|
| patientId | int | body | Yes | Patient ID |
| items | array | body | Yes | Array of {medicineId, dosage, quantity} |

**Response:** `201 Created`: Prescription ID

### `GET /api/pharmacy/prescriptions`
*(US-PAT 05, US-PHR 05)* Patient sees their prescriptions, Pharmacist sees pending.
**Response:** `200 OK`: Array of prescriptions

### `DELETE /api/pharmacy/prescriptions/:prescriptionId/items/:itemId`
*(US-PHR 07)* Remove a medicine from a prescription.
**Response:** `204 No Content`

### `PUT /api/pharmacy/prescriptions/:prescriptionId/dispense`
*(US-PHR 06)* Mark prescription as 'dispensed' & trigger inventory reduction.
**Response:** `200 OK`: Status updated

### `GET /api/pharmacy/cost/:prescriptionId`
*(US-PHR 09)* See full price of dispensed medicine.
**Response:** `200 OK`: `{ "totalMedicineCost": 150.00 }`

---

## 7. Invoices & Revenue (`/api/finance`)

### `GET /api/finance/invoices/:patientId`
*(US-PAT 04)* Patient checks invoices and tracks payments.
**Response:** `200 OK`: Array of invoice history

### `GET /api/finance/visit-cost/:appointmentId`
*(US-PHR 10)* See total cost for a patient's visit (lab, appt, medicine).
**Response:** `200 OK`: `{ "totalCost": 450.00, "breakdown": {...} }`

### `GET /api/finance/revenue/stats`
*(US-DOC 01)* Check doctor revenue.
**Parameters:**
| Name | Type | In | Required | Description |
|------|------|----|----------|-------------|
| period | string | query | Yes | 'daily', 'monthly', 'annual' |

**Response:** `200 OK`: `{ "revenue": 1450.50 }`

